<div class="post-4 page type-page status-publish hentry fpost" id="post-4">
				
				
				
					  	
						<div class="entry_wrap fix">
						
							<div class="entry_content">
								<p><a href="https://github.com/bloom-lang/bud/blob/v0.0.3/docs/getstarted.md"><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-119" title="simple chat server" src="http://www.bloom-lang.net/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/chatserver.png" alt="" width="290" height="258" /></a></p>
<p>Bloom is a language &#8230;</p>
<p>&#8230; for disorderly distributed programming<br />
<em><span style="color: gray;">because order is expensive</span></em></p>
<p>&#8230; with powerful consistency analysis<br />
<em><span style="color: gray;">CALM guidance on coordination</span></em></p>
<p>&#8230; and concise, familiar syntax<br />
<em><span style="color: gray;">based on data-centric languages</span></em></p>
<a class = "github-ribbon" href="https://github.com/bloom-lang/bud"><img style="position: fixed; top: 0; right: 0; border: 0;" src="http://s3.amazonaws.com/github/ribbons/forkme_right_darkblue_121621.png" alt="Fork me on GitHub" /></a>									<div class="clear"></div> 
																</div>	
							<div class="tags">
								&nbsp;
							</div>
						</div>
								</div>

	<div class="clear"></div>
	</div>
